{"tid":2355352,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(正視聽) 慎防失敗主義","createTime":"2021-01-06T05:20:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T05:42:52.000Z","uid":270170,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b4b1e96abbf3fc4ff2fd865e2b391b9f708aeec8","tid":2355352,"uid":270170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T05:20:13.000Z","msg":"又到月經post既時間，啲乜撚本土線已完啊認輸啊移民啊出晒黎<br />\n<br />\n1. 本土線未完: 本土線只有你話完既一刻先會完，比人拉既都未放棄，我地仲生勾勾既憑咩？<br />\n2. 移民中共就最開心: 中共最想就係大家移民。留島不留人聽過啦？過到去生小朋友，過多幾代，再冇人知道Hong Kong，只有xianggang。<br />\n3. 認輸？食慒左啊？: 而家係革命，認輸既後果有冇諗過？冇既話去睇下人地輸左既革命係點，例如馬來亞共產黨打輸左仗走入邊境森林潛伏20年，孟加拉獨立運動既大屠殺。認輸唔係講兩隻字之後返去平淡生活。輸得起咩？<br />\n<br />\n政治層面上可能舉步維艱，但文化層面上我地仲有好多野要守護: 廣東話、歷史建築、你樓下食開既茶餐廳、黃店，仲有好多好多。就算我地呢一刻未儲夠勇氣再係政治革命上行出黎，我地仲有好多工作要做。<br />\n<br />\n慎防失敗撚。"},{"pid":"3707c0fcd310678b7f92a35e3f55cca9453e9db2","tid":2355352,"uid":270170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T05:20:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"75ca26eff791af1f9185e7b18aeee0e48cee9c3f","tid":2355352,"uid":270170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T05:20:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b2d6b36c941c67c7d2a06f5fd7453fa838ead0c4","tid":2355352,"uid":270170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T05:21:11.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef576d8cb8632349411369669d22fed7504cd9cf","tid":2355352,"uid":270170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T05:21:45.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d3326311f1692be61413362c08e82be45a8d66a","tid":2355352,"uid":270170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T05:22:20.000Z","msg":"推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass